2
00:00:02,929 --> 00:00:04,858
(Kim Min Ha)

3
00:00:04,859 --> 00:00:06,929
(Jung Gun Joo, Oh Woo Ri, Ko Chang Seok, Seo Young Hee)

4
00:00:09,869 --> 00:00:13,009
(Way Back Love)

5
00:00:21,409 --> 00:00:22,978
(Danger)

6
00:00:22,979 --> 00:00:24,379
(Stop)

7
00:00:28,649 --> 00:00:29,689
