701
00:38:47,217 --> 00:38:49,056
- Ram Woo! - Kim Ram Woo!

702
00:38:49,057 --> 00:38:50,386
Jung Hee Wan!

703
00:38:50,387 --> 00:38:51,927
Kim Ram Woo! Jung Hee Wan!

704
00:38:52,057 --> 00:38:53,987
